  <brief_title>Randomized Controlled Trial of Calcitriol vs. Placebo Among Critically-ill Patients With Sepsis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized Controlled Trial of Calcitriol vs. Placebo Among Critically-ill Patients With Sepsis</official_title>
